{"tid":1721333,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[純學術討論] 簡易防彈衣","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:58:05.000Z","uid":115286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57120b3475ac470c12d43d6bb89d8ba3455e394d","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"事源我碌youtube碌到依條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dCvKycPNCfc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdCvKycPNCfc&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6x%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=872dd744\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dCvKycPNCfc</a><br />\n佢壓到一疊廁紙勁實用黎試擋子彈 但結果係失敗嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁youtube recommend佢第2條片 係用鋁板<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1sPbMdrzFJU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1sPbMdrzFJU&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6x%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=b159995a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1sPbMdrzFJU</a><br />\n結果係打唔穿 但會斷肋骨 鋁板加工又好似好麻煩 著上身行動又唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我見到第一條片有個留言就推介第2個youtuber嘅片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_7jiIQOgwtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_7jiIQOgwtI&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6x%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=8ef37d32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_7jiIQOgwtI</a><br />\n估唔到用幾塊30幾蚊嘅防火毯痴埋 壓實就可以擋子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到我眼都突埋 有無物理友解釋下可唔可行<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識物理 純學野"},{"pid":"2a4843c3daf75c17ee140f69c2e18e30b84a2ae1","tid":1721333,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8078e239b3a511d7589c425cc0d910d1685121ed","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"c68abda1b916380cccfd6463728daa2117e3712b","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"推二推"},{"pid":"20dc9dc0b2970e5ed087164940e919adfa6324eb","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"推三推"},{"pid":"69254993f812f4737899e79d3cf01f44a393f38a","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"推四推"},{"pid":"ee2b1df8faa22b6b896f0e92378c9877241d8ce3","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"推五推"},{"pid":"72048b785d041250000a3907d1b4ec626eba6c3f","tid":1721333,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"撞擊時間愈長, 愈可以卸力<br />\n所以避彈衣入面會加軟墊, 同埋夾層, 好過就咁一塊鐵<br />\n用遮檔橡膠子彈原理一樣"},{"pid":"a58da049ac71992dc87fd6ed1f2e51f1479d8405","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"推六推"},{"pid":"0171b6279c421dbe3438954da97ccc6d877b4176","tid":1721333,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"推七推"},{"pid":"35f7789eb262bfdba1c2b81c7b901d54e4a25807","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0171b6279c421dbe3438954da97ccc6d877b4176","tid":1721333,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"推七推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"推八推"},{"pid":"31958458ce6cdd6dc29f6dde5eaa43ede7584a6c","tid":1721333,"uid":115286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl